1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,040
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman">September 5th, 2045</font></font>

2
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're off.</font>

3
00:00:04,970 --> 00:00:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you later.</font>

4
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care.</font>

5
00:00:09,630 --> 00:00:10,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

6
00:00:11,170 --> 00:00:12,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for driving.</font>

7
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:13,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go, go!</font>

8
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're gone.</font>

9
00:00:28,830 --> 00:00:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, is there anything I can do to help?</font>

10
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. You'd just get in the way.</font>

11
00:00:36,680 --> 00:00:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But school has started for 
Saionji-san, Akari, and Riku-san.</font>

12
00:00:41,970 --> 00:00:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Rui-chan, 
don't you have school?</font>

13
00:00:45,350 --> 00:00:47,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm already dead.</font>

14
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

15
00:00:48,110 --> 00:00:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're an important part of our forces.</font>

16
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should train to improve 
your spirit power.</font>

17
00:00:53,610 --> 00:00:55,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Train? How?</font>

18
00:00:56,070 --> 00:00:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ask Dad.</font>

19
00:00:58,890 --> 00:01:00,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dad?</font>

20
00:01:03,810 --> 00:01:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one's told you yet.</font>

21
00:01:05,980 --> 00:01:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yukihito Miyata, 47 years old, 
also known as Settei the monk.</font>

22
00:01:11,250 --> 00:01:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He is my father.</font>

23
00:01:12,790 --> 00:01:14,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're kidding, right?</font>

24
00:01:15,420 --> 00:01:19,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why does "music" exist in this world?</i></font>

25
00:01:19,770 --> 00:01:28,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think I've figured it out</i></font>

26
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This melody will go on living 
much, much longer than us</i></font>

27
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:49,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For thousands and tens 
of thousands of years</i></font>

28
00:01:49,290 --> 00:01:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Carrying the flames of wishes past</i></font>

29
00:01:53,080 --> 00:01:55,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Traveling across time</i></font>

30
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What color is your elegy?</i></font>

31
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well? Tell me</i></font>

32
00:02:03,120 --> 00:02:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My 1,000% pure curiosity</i></font>

33
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can't be stopped</i></font>

34
00:02:11,130 --> 00:02:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let my heart sing, sing, sing, 
sing and turn my life into music</i></font>

35
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I despise the word "destiny"</i></font>

36
00:02:20,660 --> 00:02:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ghosts still believe in pure dreams</i></font>

37
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just as everyone's souls scream</i></font>

38
00:02:27,030 --> 00:02:31,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The racing ba-dump, ba-dump, ba-dump, 
ba-dump running through the present</i></font>

39
00:02:31,620 --> 00:02:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Waltzes through the new
 world with enough force</i></font>

40
00:02:34,440 --> 00:02:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to break through the afterlife's border</i></font>

41
00:02:38,130 --> 00:02:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now smile and shine</i></font>

42
00:02:45,510 --> 00:02:46,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not kidding.</font>

43
00:02:46,890 --> 00:02:48,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we're not blood-related.</font>

44
00:02:50,450 --> 00:02:51,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're adopted?</font>

45
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something like that.</font>

46
00:02:57,810 --> 00:03:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long ago, I lived on another island.</font>

47
00:03:02,180 --> 00:03:08,080
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman">5 Years Ago, 2040</font></font>

48
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The island is a closed society.</font>

49
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:08,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It has no official name and isn't on maps.</font>

50
00:03:08,500 --> 00:03:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The island's ancient custom</font>

51
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:16,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is to sacrifice a young girl to the evil 
god that resides there as a pure bride.</font>

52
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brides are imprisoned in 
a cage at a small shrine.</font>

53
00:03:22,770 --> 00:03:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In reality, there is no evil god.</font>

54
00:03:25,210 --> 00:03:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a necessary political 
practice to ensure the residents</font>

55
00:03:29,350 --> 00:03:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't lose their faith.</font>

56
00:03:33,730 --> 00:03:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The practice is also used</font>

57
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to punish squabbling nobles and 
anyone plotting rebellion.</font>

58
00:03:40,690 --> 00:03:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daughters of traitorous nobles 
are sacrificed as brides.</font>

59
00:03:49,390 --> 00:03:53,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was purchased to take the 
place of one such daughter.</font>

60
00:03:57,070 --> 00:04:00,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was remade to look exactly like her.</font>

61
00:04:01,690 --> 00:04:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I no longer remember what 
I actually look like.</font>

62
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's awful.</font>

63
00:04:06,070 --> 00:04:08,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After their sixth new moon,</font>

64
00:04:08,220 --> 00:04:12,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">girls chosen to be brides 
are consumed by the evil god</font>

65
00:04:12,790 --> 00:04:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and vanish without a trace.</font>

66
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:17,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Consumed?</font>

67
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're simply killed.</font>

68
00:04:20,210 --> 00:04:24,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was merely a tool to control people.</font>

69
00:04:24,370 --> 00:04:26,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you end up here?</font>

70
00:04:27,140 --> 00:04:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was possessed by the spirits 
of the previous sacrifices.</font>

71
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:31,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Possessed?</font>

72
00:04:31,870 --> 00:04:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like you.</font>

73
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:36,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't do what you do.</font>

74
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't control the 
spirits that possessed me.</font>

75
00:04:43,380 --> 00:04:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I escaped from the shrine and 
rampaged through the town.</font>

76
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:58,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At their wit's end, the nobles hired an 
esoteric Buddhist order to eliminate me.</font>

77
00:04:58,730 --> 00:05:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was nearly killed by practitioners 
as part of their training.</font>

78
00:05:04,780 --> 00:05:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But one of them saved me.</font>

79
00:05:08,670 --> 00:05:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean the monk?</font>

80
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:12,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've been together ever since.</font>

81
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He taught me to speak and helped 
me figure out how to create these.</font>

82
00:05:17,540 --> 00:05:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your stitched spirit beasts.</font>

83
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:23,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He even gave me a name and 
did my hair like this.</font>

84
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe this makes me me.</font>

85
00:05:26,790 --> 00:05:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for telling me.</font>

86
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why tell me something so important?</font>

87
00:05:32,530 --> 00:05:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since I was born, the only music 
in this world has been MiucS'.</font>

88
00:05:56,870 --> 00:06:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt like I'd heard real 
music for the first time.</font>

89
00:06:00,380 --> 00:06:02,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, shucks.</font>

90
00:06:02,060 --> 00:06:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be killed if I sing.</font>

91
00:06:04,090 --> 00:06:07,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I can't sing like you.</font>

92
00:06:07,370 --> 00:06:09,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to learn to sing like you.</font>

93
00:06:11,690 --> 00:06:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure you will someday.</font>

94
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I meant it when I said you're a key 
part of our forces, but that's not all.</font>

95
00:06:18,950 --> 00:06:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to hear you sing more, so...</font>

96
00:06:23,170 --> 00:06:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'll get stronger 
and train for you, too.</font>

97
00:06:27,610 --> 00:06:30,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And for the monk... for your father.</font>

98
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Twenty-two.</font>

99
00:06:33,450 --> 00:06:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Twenty-three, twenty-four.</font>

100
00:06:37,590 --> 00:06:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Twenty-five.</font>

101
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, he's back.</font>

102
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Seria?</font>

103
00:06:48,630 --> 00:06:50,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back, Settei-san.</font>

104
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to become stronger.</font>

105
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should I do?</font>

106
00:06:54,770 --> 00:06:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to train?</font>

107
00:06:56,660 --> 00:06:59,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, you don't need to do that.</font>

108
00:06:59,020 --> 00:07:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why not?</font>

109
00:07:00,500 --> 00:07:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The spirits that possess 
you are too strong.</font>

110
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:06,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And while an ordinary medium</font>

111
00:07:06,530 --> 00:07:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would need to increase their 
spiritual and physical strength,</font>

112
00:07:09,450 --> 00:07:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your own spirit power is quite high.</font>

113
00:07:12,470 --> 00:07:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the Phantom Realm, spirit power 
matters more than flesh and blood.</font>

114
00:07:16,260 --> 00:07:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you're reasonably 
fit, you'll be fine.</font>

115
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

116
00:07:21,420 --> 00:07:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I had to say, it'd be ideal if you 
could increase your spirit medium power,</font>

117
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there's no point in letting 
any old spirit possess you.</font>

118
00:07:30,420 --> 00:07:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's not wise to carelessly venture</font>

119
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">into the Phantom Realm
without orders from TERA.</font>

120
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That storehouse serves as a library.</font>

121
00:07:39,890 --> 00:07:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A library?</font>

122
00:07:41,460 --> 00:07:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We might run into another Great Ghost.</font>

123
00:07:45,020 --> 00:07:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've got plenty of 
history books. Read them.</font>

124
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">History books? Thank you.</font>

125
00:07:50,010 --> 00:07:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it's locked.</font>

126
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:55,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get the key from Rui-chan.</font>

127
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

128
00:07:58,030 --> 00:08:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She likes history, huh? So that's why...</font>

129
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, look at all these books.</font>

130
00:08:03,500 --> 00:08:05,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can read all of these?</font>

131
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're too difficult for me.</font>

132
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is yours to use as you please.</font>

133
00:08:09,410 --> 00:08:10,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

134
00:08:11,320 --> 00:08:15,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't read books online anymore, 
and I'm getting to read paper books.</font>

135
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a note.</font>

136
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:19,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem to be having fun.</font>

137
00:08:21,170 --> 00:08:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

138
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah?</font>

139
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:28,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the food.</font>

140
00:08:28,940 --> 00:08:31,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a lot nicer than usual.</font>

141
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's good.</font>

142
00:08:34,570 --> 00:08:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seria's salary from TERA 
came in. We're celebrating.</font>

143
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Seria-chan's not here.</font>

144
00:08:40,650 --> 00:08:42,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's eating in the library.</font>

145
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she had no time to spare.</font>

146
00:08:44,370 --> 00:08:46,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She reads? I'm surprised.</font>

147
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:49,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe she's possessed by 
the evil spirit of Kinjiro.</font>

148
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry. She seems to be having fun.</font>

149
00:08:52,910 --> 00:08:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently she's always liked history.</font>

150
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:59,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? I'm glad, then.</font>

151
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:03,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#8c7c6e">Japanese History</font></font></font>

152
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:03,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font size="12"><font color="#8c7c6e">12</font></font></font>

153
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:03,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#8c7c6e">Central Government of
the Late Edo Period</font></font></font>

154
00:09:42,190 --> 00:09:44,730
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font face="Times New Roman">September 27th, 2045</font></font>

155
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that you, Yotetsu?</font>

156
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

157
00:09:46,020 --> 00:09:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you want?</font>

158
00:09:47,090 --> 00:09:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe we should prioritize 
installing that flagstone there.</font>

159
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not important to TERA's strategy, 
but it's a shortcut to MiucS.</font>

160
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's been no sign of</font>

161
00:09:58,630 --> 00:10:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">interference from other organizations 
or dark spirits for several days.</font>

162
00:10:02,270 --> 00:10:06,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that right? 
We can't sacrifice them, though.</font>

163
00:10:08,050 --> 00:10:10,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then will you disguise yourself again?</font>

164
00:10:14,900 --> 00:10:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Phantom Shift.</font>

165
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There. Now I can seduce Iemitsu.</font>

166
00:10:40,210 --> 00:10:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yotetsu, did you just 
come here to tease me?</font>

167
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:46,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, although that does sound fun.</font>

168
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Kasuga made me a deal.</font>

169
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We provide a woman Lord Iemitsu 
will invite into his bed.</font>

170
00:10:56,010 --> 00:10:58,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we do that, she'll hand over the area.</font>

171
00:10:58,460 --> 00:11:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've already secured her agreement.</font>

172
00:11:00,590 --> 00:11:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But a mere invitation won't 
fulfill Lady Kasuga's wish.</font>

173
00:11:04,850 --> 00:11:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We just need to get him 
interested in a woman to start.</font>

174
00:11:07,990 --> 00:11:12,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're exploring other ways 
to produce an heir as spirits.</font>

175
00:11:12,560 --> 00:11:16,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So, how do you 
intend to tackle this?</font>

176
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:20,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll use Seria Aiba-san. 
Wouldn't her ability be useful?</font>

177
00:11:20,320 --> 00:11:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

178
00:11:24,780 --> 00:11:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Edo Castle?</font>

179
00:11:26,100 --> 00:11:28,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Using force won't work here.</font>

180
00:11:28,470 --> 00:11:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Kasuga has agreed to hand over 
this area if we meet her conditions.</font>

181
00:11:32,350 --> 00:11:37,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Kasuga's wish is for Lord Tokugawa 
Iemitsu to express interest in a woman.</font>

182
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But aren't Saionji-san or 
Riku-san better suited for that?</font>

183
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you're the best fit.</font>

184
00:11:44,380 --> 00:11:45,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

185
00:11:46,530 --> 00:11:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

186
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right. Lord Iemitsu's 
spirit still prefers men.</font>

187
00:11:51,180 --> 00:11:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Following history, we'll send a woman 
who can disguise herself as a man.</font>

188
00:11:54,780 --> 00:11:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't mean...</font>

189
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Caesar, Antonius, Okita.</font>

190
00:11:58,630 --> 00:11:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spirit-Sync Release.</font>

191
00:12:01,770 --> 00:12:03,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't drag us out like that.</font>

192
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:05,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a problem.</font>

193
00:12:05,490 --> 00:12:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But we understand the situation.</font>

194
00:12:07,580 --> 00:12:10,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seria, we'll help you. Right?</font>

195
00:12:10,390 --> 00:12:11,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we must.</font>

196
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's give it a shot.</font>

197
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

198
00:12:17,300 --> 00:12:19,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What just happened?</font>

199
00:12:19,570 --> 00:12:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad, right?</font>

200
00:12:27,290 --> 00:12:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad.</font>

201
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But Seria,</font>

202
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your charms alone may not be enough 
to make Lord Iemitsu fall for you.</font>

203
00:12:34,780 --> 00:12:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think so?</font>

204
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you need help, call me.</font>

205
00:12:38,770 --> 00:12:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not test our feminine charms?</font>

206
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We appreciate the help.</font>

207
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no concern about Lady Kasuga</font>

208
00:12:46,050 --> 00:12:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">discovering the male spirits 
and complaining about it.</font>

209
00:12:49,910 --> 00:12:54,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. I'm not too confident, 
but if that's what you want, Cleo...</font>

210
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

211
00:12:57,450 --> 00:12:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, we'll achieve a high 
enough rank for an audience.</font>

212
00:12:59,690 --> 00:13:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will being here really help with that?</font>

213
00:13:02,370 --> 00:13:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It might be hard to get 
the shogun's attention</font>

214
00:13:05,540 --> 00:13:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without being adopted by a daimyo.</font>

215
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Kasuga has deviated 
from historical fact.</font>

216
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:14,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She grants opportunities 
to those who work hard.</font>

217
00:13:14,770 --> 00:13:18,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That said, I don't 
have any special skills.</font>

218
00:13:18,610 --> 00:13:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll help you establish a positive record.</font>

219
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Rui-chan.</font>

220
00:13:23,910 --> 00:13:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll do everything we 
can without being rude.</font>

221
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

222
00:13:31,370 --> 00:13:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're done here. 
We'll head over there next.</font>

223
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could it be?</font>

224
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How truly beautiful.</font>

225
00:13:44,950 --> 00:13:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the girls sent by Settei-dono?</font>

226
00:13:49,230 --> 00:13:50,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Seria Aiba.</font>

227
00:13:50,730 --> 00:13:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rui.</font>

228
00:13:51,630 --> 00:13:56,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. Raise your heads, Oseri and Orui.</font>

229
00:13:59,190 --> 00:14:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Kasuga no Tsubone.</font>

230
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I run the inner palace on 
behalf of the shogun's wife.</font>

231
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:10,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you can see, there are 
many maidservants here.</font>

232
00:14:10,510 --> 00:14:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though you were sent by Settei-dono,</font>

233
00:14:13,410 --> 00:14:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">gaining an audience will 
still be difficult</font>

234
00:14:15,880 --> 00:14:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as you're not daughters of bannermen.</font>

235
00:14:19,010 --> 00:14:25,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must also judge if you're 
worthy of the shogun.</font>

236
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:26,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, milady.</font>

237
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:29,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very good. Now, if you'll excuse me.</font>

238
00:14:29,750 --> 00:14:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. The girl assigned to clean 
the bathhouse is sick in bed today.</font>

239
00:14:35,010 --> 00:14:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oseri, could you do it for her?</font>

240
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bathhouse? As you wish.</font>

241
00:14:45,650 --> 00:14:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seria?</font>

242
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is an opportunity for us.</font>

243
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Iemitsu had an affair with 
Lady Onatsu in the bathhouse.</font>

244
00:14:52,330 --> 00:14:56,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's a chance to interact with Iemitsu 
without achieving a higher rank.</font>

245
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:59,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if he makes a pass at me...</font>

246
00:14:59,220 --> 00:15:00,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me handle that.</font>

247
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cleo?</font>

248
00:15:01,580 --> 00:15:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trust me to handle such matters.</font>

249
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:08,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm far better at handling men.</font>

250
00:15:08,280 --> 00:15:10,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true, but...</font>

251
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We shall preserve your chastity.</font>

252
00:15:13,220 --> 00:15:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he makes advances, 
we can brush him off.</font>

253
00:15:17,900 --> 00:15:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

254
00:15:22,180 --> 00:15:24,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-How is the water?</font>

255
00:15:25,550 --> 00:15:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not bad.</font>

256
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:28,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

257
00:15:32,620 --> 00:15:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing? 
Hurry up and wipe me down.</font>

258
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My apologies.</font>

259
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something wrong? Have I offended you?</font>

260
00:15:58,940 --> 00:16:00,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you haven't.</font>

261
00:16:00,470 --> 00:16:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough. I'm getting out.</font>

262
00:16:02,380 --> 00:16:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, milord.</font>

263
00:16:04,710 --> 00:16:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raise your head.</font>

264
00:16:16,620 --> 00:16:17,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did well.</font>

265
00:16:17,780 --> 00:16:21,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He knows who you are now, 
and we confirmed his preferences.</font>

266
00:16:21,050 --> 00:16:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't let it get to you.</font>

267
00:16:23,250 --> 00:16:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were told he's not interested in women.</font>

268
00:16:26,170 --> 00:16:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, but...</font>

269
00:16:27,430 --> 00:16:29,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should move on to our next strategy.</font>

270
00:16:29,610 --> 00:16:31,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'm doing this for Cleo, too.</i></font>

271
00:16:31,250 --> 00:16:35,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll do whatever it takes to climb 
the ladder and make him fall for me.</i></font>

272
00:16:31,550 --> 00:16:33,050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Low-ranking Maid</font>

273
00:16:33,050 --> 00:16:34,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Gate Watch</font>

274
00:16:34,550 --> 00:16:36,050
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Fire Watch</font>

275
00:16:36,050 --> 00:16:37,550
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Tea Room Maid</font>

276
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:39,060
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Kitchen Maid</font>

277
00:16:39,060 --> 00:16:40,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">Living Room Maid</font>

278
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for you.</font>

279
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

280
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:48,940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an7}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#282e25"><font size="20">You are hereby permitted to
receive an audience with the shogun.
Do not take the honor lightly.</font></font></b></font></font>

281
00:16:49,230 --> 00:16:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it really okay for me to 
wear something so beautiful?</font>

282
00:16:53,150 --> 00:16:55,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It suits you, Oseri-sama.</font>

283
00:16:55,780 --> 00:16:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad.</font>

284
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please excuse us.</font>

285
00:17:02,520 --> 00:17:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Starting tomorrow, you'll attend 
the general announcement.</font>

286
00:17:04,330 --> 00:17:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your chance will come when Iemitsu 
scans everyone in attendance.</font>

287
00:17:07,630 --> 00:17:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. Follow the plan.</font>

288
00:17:44,520 --> 00:17:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is your name?</font>

289
00:17:47,260 --> 00:17:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, my.</font>

290
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:50,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes!</i></font>

291
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Great!</i></font>

292
00:17:51,460 --> 00:17:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Of course.</i></font>

293
00:17:54,670 --> 00:17:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, why? I thought he just 
had to invite me into his bed.</font>

294
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't let you leave now.</font>

295
00:18:03,870 --> 00:18:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not doing this.</font>

296
00:18:06,860 --> 00:18:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case...</font>

297
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:12,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bloodshed is strictly forbidden 
in the inner palace.</font>

298
00:18:12,980 --> 00:18:16,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Agreements cannot be broken either.</font>

299
00:18:16,190 --> 00:18:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

300
00:18:17,420 --> 00:18:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oseri, you caught the shogun's attention.</font>

301
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ask that you bear his children.</font>

302
00:18:23,990 --> 00:18:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No...</font>

303
00:18:25,230 --> 00:18:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, come.</font>

304
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

305
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

306
00:18:30,940 --> 00:18:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something must've happened.</font>

307
00:18:32,500 --> 00:18:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

308
00:18:33,500 --> 00:18:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

309
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What should I do?</i></font>

310
00:18:38,050 --> 00:18:41,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't do much if you're 
unable to wield swords.</font>

311
00:18:42,040 --> 00:18:43,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't what we agreed to.</font>

312
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:45,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were told we only need to be invited.</font>

313
00:18:45,680 --> 00:18:47,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow us to possess you.</font>

314
00:18:47,450 --> 00:18:49,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will defend your chastity.</font>

315
00:18:49,390 --> 00:18:54,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But we need this area to reach 
MiucS, and he's just a ghost.</i></font>

316
00:18:54,300 --> 00:19:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Besides, I'm basically dead, right? I...</i></font>

317
00:19:01,110 --> 00:19:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then we should steel ourselves as well.</font>

318
00:19:03,620 --> 00:19:04,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

319
00:19:05,370 --> 00:19:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seria, get a hold of yourself.</font>

320
00:19:11,420 --> 00:19:14,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-This is... You may pass.</font>

321
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:15,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you.</font>

322
00:19:17,130 --> 00:19:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're ready for you, milord.</font>

323
00:19:20,340 --> 00:19:21,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

324
00:19:27,810 --> 00:19:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me see your face.</font>

325
00:19:30,140 --> 00:19:31,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, milord.</font>

326
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sorry, guys.</i></font>

327
00:19:40,040 --> 00:19:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's all right. You're doing well.</i></font>

328
00:19:43,250 --> 00:19:44,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it.</font>

329
00:19:45,090 --> 00:19:45,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

330
00:19:45,950 --> 00:19:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We met previously in the bathhouse.</font>

331
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:51,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You thought you could 
outwit me? How laughable.</font>

332
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What trick are you using? Show me.</font>

333
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

334
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't do that.</i></font>

335
00:19:57,710 --> 00:20:01,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? That will do.</font>

336
00:20:01,100 --> 00:20:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come closer.</font>

337
00:20:02,760 --> 00:20:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? N-No, wait.</font>

338
00:20:05,870 --> 00:20:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The shogun's orders cannot 
be defied. This isn't good.</i></font>

339
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We have bigger problems right now.</i></font>

340
00:20:10,930 --> 00:20:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have steeled my resolve.</i></font>

341
00:20:18,520 --> 00:20:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I come.</font>

342
00:20:19,540 --> 00:20:20,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

343
00:20:22,100 --> 00:20:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you?</font>

344
00:20:23,740 --> 00:20:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hand him over!</font>

345
00:20:26,320 --> 00:20:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

346
00:20:28,910 --> 00:20:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go.</font>

347
00:20:38,370 --> 00:20:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way.</font>

348
00:20:40,550 --> 00:20:41,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

349
00:20:43,070 --> 00:20:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milord? Oseri, after them!</font>

350
00:20:45,670 --> 00:20:47,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Uh, yes, milady!</font>

351
00:20:47,140 --> 00:20:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

352
00:20:52,190 --> 00:20:54,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Masamori? Shigezumi?</font>

353
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you came for me.</font>

354
00:20:59,430 --> 00:21:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

355
00:21:00,800 --> 00:21:02,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

356
00:21:02,990 --> 00:21:04,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I come.</font>

357
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad.</font>

358
00:21:11,160 --> 00:21:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, yeah.</font>

359
00:21:12,120 --> 00:21:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what happened after that?</font>

360
00:21:15,690 --> 00:21:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The inner palace vanished, and we 
successfully placed the Chiaku Flagstone.</font>

361
00:21:19,550 --> 00:21:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, I wonder who that page was.</font>

362
00:21:22,760 --> 00:21:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't know.</font>

363
00:21:24,890 --> 00:21:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd probably recognize him if he 
were a famous historical figure.</font>

364
00:21:29,010 --> 00:21:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was he really that handsome?</font>

365
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably?</font>

366
00:21:34,730 --> 00:21:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What does that mean?</font>

367
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:38,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The circumstances probably 
made him 30% hotter.</font>

368
00:21:38,980 --> 00:21:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe, but I'll have to thank 
him if I see him again.</font>

369
00:21:44,710 --> 00:21:46,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like "Much Ado About Love"?!</font>

370
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, we achieved our goal.</font>

371
00:21:54,850 --> 00:21:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the help, Seria and Rui.</font>

372
00:21:58,550 --> 00:21:59,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir.</font>

373
00:22:05,510 --> 00:22:09,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24"><font size="18"><font color="#26272d">Yukihito Miyata</font></font></font>

374
00:22:06,290 --> 00:22:09,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Thank you, Settei-san.</i></font>

375
00:22:20,150 --> 00:22:23,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ah, clearing a path even 
though I'm not certain</i></font>

376
00:22:23,940 --> 00:22:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Advancing towards a faint light</i></font>

377
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ah, on this path of thorns</i></font>

378
00:22:35,430 --> 00:22:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To prevent the pain 
from wilting our hearts</i></font>

379
00:22:44,320 --> 00:22:48,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We pray</i></font>

380
00:23:12,240 --> 00:23:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Buffeted by headwinds</i></font>

381
00:23:15,180 --> 00:23:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The harder it is to walk</i></font>

382
00:23:18,460 --> 00:23:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The less we're bothered 
by this path of thorns</i></font>

383
00:23:25,320 --> 00:23:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Fly freely up into that sky</i></font>

384
00:23:30,580 --> 00:23:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It will surely be a delight, 
now break your fate</i></font>

